						<td colspan="2" style="">&nbsp;
						<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Dear </span><strong>{!Opportunity.Project_Coordinator__c}</strong>,</p>

						<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 40px;">We&rsquo;d like to inform you that <strong><a href="https://na29.salesforce.com/{!Opportunity.Id}">{!Opportunity.Name}</a></strong> will receive an Installation survey invitation from SunPower in 10 days.<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 40px;">The survey covers various aspects of the sales and installation process and includes the &ldquo;Likelihood to Recommend&rdquo; question that is used to calculate Net Promoter Score (NPS).<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 40px;">Before the survey is sent we&rsquo;d like to suggest some best practice steps that you can take to help increase your response rate and overall customer satisfaction:<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=""><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Check that the system is fully operational including monitoring if applicable<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=""><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Conduct a final walkthrough of the system with the homeowner (if not done previously),<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=""><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ensure that all remaining issues and homeowner concerns have been resolved <o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=""><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Let the homeowner know that a survey will be coming from SunPower and that you&rsquo;d appreciate their response.</p>

						<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 40px;">As a reminder the surveys invitations are sent to homeowners with valid email addresses under the following conditions:<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Cash</span>: &nbsp;10 days after Online Warranty Registration is completed<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; font-style: italic; margin-left: 80px;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=""><span style="">-<span style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Lease</span>:&nbsp; 10 days after the system is &ldquo;Placed in Service&rdquo; (system is commissioned, grid connected and operational)<o:p></o:p></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 40px;"></p>

						<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 40px;"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Warm regards,<br />
						Your SunPower Team</b></p>
